metadata.name: Chromatic Elegance
metadata.description: AI output image from Wombo AI then post processed with analog glitch utilities. In this instance the equipment used was a Tachyons+ Opti-glitch, connected to a Somfey Spectraloom and out to a Sanyo TV. This was then rescanned with a Olympus OMD-EM10 Mark III and finished in Affinity photo.
